<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">所谓首异，是指两个因数十位上的数字不同；所谓尾合，即两个因数个位上的数字和为10.此法，可先将被乘数分解，然后分别与乘数相乘，最后将两组和相加，即得所求之积。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">46×34=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 46×34</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=100×4×6+100×6+6×6</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=2400+600+36</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=3000+36</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=3036</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>